Lectura de la base de datos

ICFES201502 <- read.csv2("20152.csv", skip = 5)
ICFES201502_1 <- droplevels(subset(ICFES201502, (JORNADA %in% 
                          c("COMPLETA U ORDINARIA","MA√ëANA","TARDE")) &
                          CALENDARIO == "A"))
limitesQ <- quantile(ICFES201502_1$EVALUADOS)
ICFES201502_1$Cat_evaluados <- cut(ICFES201502_1$EVALUADOS, limitesQ,
                                   include.lowest = TRUE)
require(ggplot2)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
coloresR <- topo.colors(4)
g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502_1, aes(PROMMATEMATICA, PROMLECTURACRITICA))
g1 + geom_point(aes(col = Cat_evaluados), alpha = 0.5) + 
     coord_fixed(1) +
     scale_colour_manual(values = coloresR, 
                         name = "Categoria evaluados") 

pairs(subset(ICFES201502_1, 
               select = PROMLECTURACRITICA:PROMCOMPETENCIASCIUDADAN))

cp1 <- princomp(subset(ICFES201502_1, 
               select = PROMLECTURACRITICA:PROMCOMPETENCIASCIUDADAN),
               cor = FALSE)
